HEADWORD: Self-neglecting
<hw>Self`-neg*lect"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
neglecting of one's self, or of one's own interests.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Self-love, my liege, is not so vile a sin⟦br⟧
As <qex>self-neglecting</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Selfness</ent>⟦br⟧
